overview: A lifetime of innocent fun together can’t stop the darkness from creeping in.  Every summer break, Jess, her older brother Trav, and their friend Kelsey spend all their time together. When the others sneak off for a party one night, Jess slowly realises that the trio will never be the same.
tagline: A lifetime of innocent fun together can’t stop the darkness from creeping in.
title: Triple Swear
